Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:17.19,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What did you make of the head priest?}Chú đã làm gì linh mục trưởng?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:21.47,Default,B,0,0,0,,{He's still young, but for a blue robe, \Nhe has a decent look in his eyes.}Vẫn còn trẻ nhưng lại được mang áo choàng xanh, khá là thiện cảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:22.97,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wait, what? Young?}Cái gì? Trẻ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:26.45,Default,B,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I bet he's around \Ntwenty-two or twenty-three.}Phải, chắc cậu ta tầm 22 hoặc 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:30.20,Default,M,0,0,0,,{No way! I was sure he was in his thirties!}Đùa à? Cháu tưởng 30?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.44,Default,B,0,0,0,,{Don't you dare let that slip in front of him.}Này, đừng có nói cho hắn biết đấy.
